                "description": {
                    "chat": "",
                    "unidentified": "",
                    "value": "<p>The faintly moving images compel one creature within 30 feet of the room to move into the room. The creature attempts a <span data-pf2-saving-throw=\"will\" data-pf2-dc=\"38\" data-pf2-traits=\"enchantment,incapacitation,mental,occult,custom\" data-pf2-label=\"Captivate DC\" data-pf2-show-dc=\"gm\">Will</span> save.</p>\n<hr />\n<p><strong>Success</strong>: The target is unaffected.</p>\n<p><strong>Failure</strong>: The target must spend all its actions on its next turn moving into the room, and is then @Compendium[pf2e.conditionitems.Paralyzed]{Paralyzed} until the end of its next turn.</p>\n<p><strong>Critical Failure</strong>: As failure, and the target is also @Compendium[pf2e.conditionitems.Stupefied]{Stupefied} 2 for 1 minute.</p>"
